    <string name="tentang_aplikasi">
        Laundry Calculator has evolved into a comprehensive laundry history management application.\n\n
        Beyond instantly calculating estimated costs based on weight, service type, and ironing options,
        this app now allows users to save, update, and manage their transaction records locally using a robust database.\n\n
        Personalize your experience! You can dynamically switch between Light/Dark themes and customize your
        viewing layout (List or Grid) according to your preferences.\n\n
        Built with modern Android Architecture (Kotlin, Jetpack Compose, Room Database, and DataStore),
        this application guarantees a fast, seamless, and user-friendly experience.
    </string>
